<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="prospect-n">prospect <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'prɒspekt/    美 /'prɑːspekt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 可能性；预期；设想：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was overjoyed at the <strong>prospect of visiting</strong> Paris.
一想到要去巴黎，她就开心得不得了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] [用复数] 前景；前途：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>job / career prospects</strong>
职业前景</p></div>

<h4 id="3c">3.<strong>[C] [正式用语] 视野；景色：</strong></h4></div>